Event.Message: The event logging service encountered an error %1 while obtaining or processing configuration for channel %2.

Event.Message: The event logging service encountered an error (%1) while enabling publisher %3 to channel %2. This does not affect channel operation, but does affect the ability of the publisher to raise events to the channel. One common reason for this error is that the Provider is using ETW Provider Security and has not granted enable permissions to the Event Log service identity.
